"title": "5392: linen",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5392: linen",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Fine cloth woven from flax used in clothing and curtains. It was also used in burials.</p>\n<h2>People dressed in linen</h2>\n<h3>Linen clothing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:12-Judg14:13\">JDG 14:12–14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:1\">JER 13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:5\">HOS 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:9\">HOS 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:51\">MRK 14:51</a></p>\n<h3>It expresssed prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:42\">GEN 41:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:15\">EST 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:23\">ISA 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19\">LUK 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:16\">REV 18:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:8\">REV 19:8</a></p>\n<h3>It was worn by priests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:23\">LEV 16:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:42\">EXO 28:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:10\">LEV 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:32\">LEV 16:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1SA 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:18\">1SA 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14\">2SA 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:27\">1CH 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:12\">2CH 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:17-Ezek44:18\">EZK 44:17–44:18</a></p>\n<h3>It was worn by angelic visitors</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:6\">REV 15:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:2-Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:2–9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:11\">EZK 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:2\">EZK 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:6-Ezek10:7\">EZK 10:6–10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:3\">EZK 40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:5\">DAN 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:6-Dan12:7\">DAN 12:6–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:8\">REV 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:14\">REV 19:14</a></p>\n<h2>Linen as an offering</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:3-Exod25:4\">EXO 25:3–25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5-Exod35:6\">EXO 35:5–35:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:23\">EXO 35:23</a></p>\n<h2>Linen used to make things</h2>\n<h3>In the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31\">EXO 26:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:36\">EXO 26:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:9\">EXO 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:16\">EXO 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:18\">EXO 27:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:5\">EXO 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:8\">EXO 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:9\">EXO 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:16\">EXO 38:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:18\">EXO 38:18</a></p>\n<h3>Other products</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:22\">PRO 31:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:16\">PRO 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:7\">EZK 27:7</a></p>\n<h2>People skilled in working with linen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:21\">1CH 4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:35\">EXO 35:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8\">EXO 36:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:35\">EXO 36:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:37\">EXO 36:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:2\">EXO 39:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:5\">EXO 39:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8\">EXO 39:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:24\">EXO 39:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27-Exod39:29\">EXO 39:27–39:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:14\">2CH 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:9\">ISA 19:9</a></p>\n<h2>Regulations for wearing linen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:11\">DEU 22:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Linen as merchandise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:24\">PRO 31:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:12\">REV 18:12</a></p>\n<h2>Contaminated linen</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:47-Lev13:48\">LEV 13:47–13:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:52\">LEV 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:59\">LEV 13:59</a></p>\n<h2>Linen used as grave clothes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:59\">MAT 27:59</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:53\">LUK 23:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:40\">JHN 19:40</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:12\">LUK 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:44\">JHN 11:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:5-John20:7\">JHN 20:5–20:7</a></p>",
